      "review_summary": "The PR adds Feishu drive list cursor inputs, scoped info lookup, optional `all` pagination, and mocked regression coverage for list/info pagination.\n\nPR surface: Source +55, Tests +213. Total +268 across 3 files.\n\nReproducibility: yes. Current main and v2026.6.8 call `drive.file.list` only once for the affected list/info paths, while the Lark SDK returns `has_more` and `next_page_token`; I did not run a live Feishu tenant in this read-only review.",
